OL,3,CMinister urges more St Helier shops to
OL,4,Copen on Sundays
OL,6,FSustainable Economic Development
OL,7,FMinister says he is "really concerned
OL,8,Fabout the number of empty shops" in
OL,9,Ftown centre.
OL,11,FDeputy Kirsten Morel wants to take a
OL,12,Fmore proactive approach in encouraging
OL,13,Foverseas businesses and those from
OL,14,Felsewhere on the island to move onto
OL,15,Fthe high street.
OL,17,FHe explains: "Obviously we're a small
OL,18,Fisland, we can't expect all retailers
OL,19,Faround the UK and Europe to know about
OL,20,FJersey so we need to go and talk to
OL,21,Fthem."
