OL,3,CMinister urges more St Helier shops to
OL,4,Copen on Sundays
OL,6,FThe minister also wants businesses
OL,7,Falready in the town centre to open
OL,8,Ftheir stores on Sundays.
OL,10,FHe adds: "If you get off the boat for
OL,11,Fa day trip and very few shops are
OL,12,Fopen, it will make you question why.
OL,13,FIf you go to St Malo, pretty much all
OL,14,Fof them are open and there's a lot to
OL,15,Fdo. In Jersey, I think we need the
OL,16,Fcentre of town to provide that."
OL,18,FDeputy Morel believes regenerating the
OL,19,Ftown centre will play a big part in
OL,20,Fmaking it more attractive.
