OL,6,FHe says Infrastructure Minister Andy
OL,7,FJehan is working with St Helier
OL,8,FConstable Simon Crowcroft on "quick
OL,9,Fwins" to revamp areas such as the
OL,10,FCentral Market as well as Broad
OL,11,FStreet, which the Government.
OL,13,FDeputy Morel also wants to put the
OL,14,Fonus on landlords and get them to
OL,15,Fjustify why stores are left vacant.
OL,17,FHe explains: "It does worry me,
OL,18,Fparticularly when I look at Queen
OL,19,FStreet, I am really concerned about
OL,20,Fthe number of empty shops up there.
