OL,6,F"If I was a tourist arriving in
OL,7,FJersey, what would I think seeing four
OL,8,For five empty stores all next to each
OL,9,Fother?
OL,11,F"There is a responsibility on
OL,12,Flandlords, we do need to remind them
OL,13,Fof that, even if they're getting rent
OL,14,Ffrom a tenant that's left, they need
OL,15,Fto get that back into trading."
